>       I am going to fit  2.2 litre 911 Porsche and 5 speed to my 73 Kombi. Has
> any one on the list done this or can you point me in the direction of any
> information on this conversion.

don't forget to upgrade your brakes and tires, and suspension to handle
the additional speed/horsepower.  my only concern is that the bus tranny
is designed for lugging and the Porsche may not have enough torque for the
extra weight....good luck

